    'estate.challenge.title': 'Managing Family Wealth Across Jurisdictions',
    'estate.challenge.body': 'Families with assets in Israel and ties to other countries face a specific challenge. Ensuring that wealth passes to the next generation efficiently, without unnecessary tax events or procedural delays. Israeli inheritance law operates under its own rules. When foreign wills or assets in multiple countries are involved, the complexity increases significantly.\n\nThe firm develops structured estate plans integrating Israeli inheritance law with relevant foreign frameworks to prevent disputes and minimise probate delays.',
    'estate.challenge.body2': '',
    'estate.wills.title': 'Wills, Succession, and Cross Border Coordination',
    'estate.wills.body': 'The firm prepares Israel specific wills and comprehensive estate plans for clients who hold assets or maintain family connections across jurisdictions. Each document is drafted to meet Israeli formal and evidentiary requirements while coordinating with any existing foreign testamentary instruments.',
    'estate.wills.compliance.title': 'Drafting for Compliance',
