    'commercial.philosophy.title': 'Precision Before Disputes',
    'commercial.philosophy.body': 'In commercial engagements, the strength of your position depends on the quality of your contracts. Whether drafting a shareholders\' agreement, negotiating an exit, or structuring a cross border arrangement, the firm evaluates each matter through three lenses. Contractual rights, financial exposure, and future enforceability.',
